<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>LinkedNetwork - Professional Networking</title>
    <style>
        /* Early 2000s Web Design */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 11px;
            background: #E8E8E8;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Header */
        #header {
            background: #003366;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #6699CC;
            padding: 8px 0;
        }

        #header-inner {
            width: 760px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        #logo {
            color: white;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            float: left;
            padding: 5px 0;
        }

        #nav {
            float: right;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        #nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            margin-left: 5px;
            background: #004080;
            border: 1px solid #6699CC;
        }

        #nav a:hover {
            background: #0066CC;
        }

        /* Main Container */
        #container {
            width: 760px;
            margin: 10px auto;
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #CCC;
        }

        /* Common Styles */
        .clear {
            clear: both;
        }

        .section {
            border: 1px solid #D0D0D0;
            margin: 10px;
            background: #F8F8F8;
        }

        .section-header {
            background: linear-gradient(#6699CC, #4477AA);
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #003366;
        }

        .section-content {
            padding: 10px;
            background: white;
        }

        /* Homepage Layout */
        #homepage-container {
            padding: 10px;
        }

        #left-column {
            float: left;
            width: 500px;
        }

        #right-column {
            float: right;
            width: 230px;
        }

        /* Stories Bar */
        #stories-bar {
            background: #F0F0F0;
            border: 1px solid #CCC;
            padding: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .story {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 60px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-right: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .story-avatar {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border: 2px solid #6699CC;
            border-radius: 25px;
            background: #DDD;
            margin: 0 auto 3px;
        }

        .story-name {
            font-size: 9px;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
        }

        /* Feed Posts */
        .post {
            border: 1px solid #D0D0D0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            background: white;
        }

        .post-header {
            background: #F5F5F5;
            padding: 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #E0E0E0;
        }

        .post-author {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #003366;
        }

        .post-time {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 10px;
        }

        .post-content {
            padding: 10px;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .post-actions {
            background: #F8F8F8;
            padding: 5px 8px;
            border-top: 1px solid #E0E0E0;
        }

        .post-actions a {
            color: #0066CC;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-right: 15px;
            font-size: 10px;
        }

        .post-actions a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Sponsored Post */
        .sponsored {
            background: #FFFFCC;
            border: 1px solid #FFCC00;
        }

        .sponsored-label {
            color: #996600;
            font-size: 9px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* People You Might Know */
        .person-suggestion {
            border-bottom: 1px dotted #CCC;
            padding: 8px 0;
        }

        .person-suggestion:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .person-avatar {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: #DDD;
            float: left;
            margin-right: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #999;
        }

        .person-info {
            float: left;
            width: 130px;
        }

        .person-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #003366;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }

        .person-title {
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .add-button {
            float: right;
            background: #6699CC;
            color: white;
            border: 1px solid #003366;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            font-size: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        /* Profile Page */
        #profile-header {
            background: linear-gradient(#F0F0F0, #E0E0E0);
            padding: 15px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #CCC;
        }

        #profile-photo {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            background: #CCC;
            border: 2px solid #999;
            float: left;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }

        #profile-info h1 {
            color: #003366;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        #profile-info .headline {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 3px;
        }

        #profile-info .location {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #999;
        }

        .profile-section {
            margin: 15px;
            border: 1px solid #D0D0D0;
        }

        .work-item, .skill-item {
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px dotted #DDD;
        }

        .work-item:last-child, .skill-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .work-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #003366;
        }

        .work-company {
            color: #666;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .work-dates {
            color: #999;
            font-size: 10px;
        }

        .skill-bar {
            background: #E0E0E0;
            height: 15px;
            margin-top: 3px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .skill-fill {
            background: #6699CC;
            height: 100%;
            position: absolute;
        }

        /* Business Page */
        #business-header {
            background: #003366;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        #business-header h1 {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        #business-header .tagline {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #CCC;
        }

        .article {
            border: 1px solid #D0D0D0;
            margin: 15px;
            background: white;
        }

        .article-header {
            background: #F5F5F5;
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #DDD;
        }

        .article-title {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #003366;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .article-meta {
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        .article-content {
            padding: 12px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .article-footer {
            background: #F8F8F8;
            padding: 8px;
            border-top: 1px solid #E0E0E0;
            font-size: 10px;
        }

        /* Tab Navigation */
        .tabs {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #CCC;
            background: #F0F0F0;
            padding: 0 10px;
        }

        .tab {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 15px;
            background: #E0E0E0;
            border: 1px solid #CCC;
            border-bottom: none;
            margin-right: 3px;
            cursor: pointer;
            position: relative;
            top: 2px;
        }

        .tab.active {
            background: white;
            border-bottom: 2px solid white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    {% include header.html %}
    {% include footer.html %}

    <!-- Homepage -->
    <div id="container">
        <div id="homepage-container">
            <!-- Left Column - Feed -->
            <div id="left-column">
                <!-- Stories -->
                <div id="stories-bar">
                    <div class="story">
                        <div class="story-avatar"></div>
                        <div class="story-name">Your Story</div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Jekyll: {% for story in site.data.stories %} -->
                    <div class="story">
                        <div class="story-avatar"></div>
                        <div class="story-name">John Smith</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="story">
                        <div class="story-avatar"></div>
                        <div class="story-name">Sarah J.</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="story">
                        <div class="story-avatar"></div>
                        <div class="story-name">Mike Chen</div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- {% endfor %} -->
                </div>

                <!-- Feed Posts -->
                <!-- Jekyll: {% for post in site.data.feed %} -->
                <div class="post">
                    <div class="post-header">
                        <span class="post-author">Robert Johnson</span>
                        <span class="post-time">2 hours ago</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="post-content">
                        Just closed a major deal with Fortune 500 client! Excited to share that our Q3 numbers are looking fantastic. Hard work pays off! #sales #success
                    </div>
                    <div class="post-actions">
                        <a href="#">Like (42)</a>
                        <a href="#">Comment (8)</a>
                        <a href="#">Share</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Sponsored Post -->
                <div class="post sponsored">
                    <div class="post-header">
                        <span class="sponsored-label">SPONSORED</span><br>
                        <span class="post-author">TechCorp Solutions</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="post-content">
                        🚀 Transform your business with our enterprise software! Join 10,000+ companies already using TechCorp. Get 30% off this month only!
                    </div>
                    <div class="post-actions">
                        <a href="#">Learn More</a>
                        <a href="#">Hide</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="post">
                    <div class="post-header">
                        <span class="post-author">Emily Davis</span>
                        <span class="post-time">5 hours ago</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="post-content">
                        Thrilled to announce I'm starting a new position as Senior Developer at Microsoft! Thanks to everyone who supported me on this journey. New chapter begins! 🎉
                    </div>
                    <div class="post-actions">
                        <a href="#">Like (156)</a>
                        <a href="#">Comment (23)</a>
                        <a href="#">Share</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- {% endfor %} -->
            </div>

            <!-- Right Column - Widgets -->
            <div id="right-column">
                <!-- People You Might Know -->
                <div class="section">
                    <div class="section-header">People You Might Know</div>
                    <div class="section-content">
                        <!-- Jekyll: {% for person in site.data.suggestions %} -->
                        <div class="person-suggestion">
                            <div class="person-avatar"></div>
                            <div class="person-info">
                                <a href="#" class="person-name">Lisa Anderson</a>
                                <div class="person-title">Marketing Director at IBM</div>
                            </div>
                            <button class="add-button">+ Add</button>
                            <div class="clear"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="person-suggestion">
                            <div class="person-avatar"></div>
                            <div class="person-info">
                                <a href="#" class="person-name">David Kim</a>
                                <div class="person-title">CTO at StartupXYZ</div>
                            </div>
                            <button class="add-button">+ Add</button>
                            <div class="clear"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="person-suggestion">
                            <div class="person-avatar"></div>
                            <div class="person-info">
                                <a href="#" class="person-name">Maria Garcia</a>
                                <div class="person-title">HR Manager</div>
                            </div>
                            <button class="add-button">+ Add</button>
                            <div class="clear"></div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- {% endfor %} -->
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Ads -->
                <div class="section">
                    <div class="section-header">Advertisement</div>
                    <div class="section-content" style="text-align: center; padding: 20px;">
                        <div style="border: 1px solid #CCC; padding: 30px; background: #F0F0F0;">
                            Your Ad Here<br>
                            200x200
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="clear"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Profile Page -->
    <div id="container" style="margin-top: 20px;">
        <div id="profile-header">
            <div id="profile-photo"></div>
            <div id="profile-info">
                <h1>{{ page.profile.name | default: "Jane Developer" }}</h1>
                <div class="headline">{{ page.profile.headline | default: "Senior Software Engineer at TechCorp" }}</div>
                <div class="location">{{ page.profile.location | default: "San Francisco Bay Area" }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="clear"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="tabs">
            <div class="tab active">Profile</div>
            <div class="tab">Activity</div>
            <div class="tab">Connections</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Work Experience -->
        <div class="profile-section">
            <div class="section-header">Work Experience</div>
            <div class="section-content">
                <!-- Jekyll: {% for job in page.profile.experience %} -->
                <div class="work-item">
                    <div class="work-title">Senior Software Engineer</div>
                    <div class="work-company">TechCorp Solutions</div>
                    <div class="work-dates">2020 - Present</div>
                    <div style="margin-top: 5px;">Leading development of cloud-based solutions. Managing team of 5 developers.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="work-item">
                    <div class="work-title">Software Developer</div>
                    <div class="work-company">StartupXYZ</div>
                    <div class="work-dates">2018 - 2020</div>
                    <div style="margin-top: 5px;">Full-stack development using React and Node.js. Implemented key features for MVP.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="work-item">
                    <div class="work-title">Junior Developer</div>
                    <div class="work-company">WebAgency Inc.</div>
                    <div class="work-dates">2016 - 2018</div>
                    <div style="margin-top: 5px;">Front-end development and maintenance of client websites.</div>
                </div>
                <!-- {% endfor %} -->
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Skills -->
        <div class="profile-section">
            <div class="section-header">Skills & Expertise</div>
            <div class="section-content">
                <!-- Jekyll: {% for skill in page.profile.skills %} -->
                <div class="skill-item">
                    <div>JavaScript</div>
                    <div class="skill-bar">
                        <div class="skill-fill" style="width: 90%"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="skill-item">
                    <div>Python</div>
                    <div class="skill-bar">
                        <div class="skill-fill" style="width: 75%"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="skill-item">
                    <div>Project Management</div>
                    <div class="skill-bar">
                        <div class="skill-fill" style="width: 80%"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="skill-item">
                    <div>Cloud Architecture</div>
                    <div class="skill-bar">
                        <div class="skill-fill" style="width: 70%"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- {% endfor %} -->
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Business Page -->
    <div id="container" style="margin-top: 20px;">
        <div id="business-header">
            <h1>{{ page.company.name | default: "TechCorp Solutions" }}</h1>
            <div class="tagline">{{ page.company.tagline | default: "Innovation Through Technology" }}</div>
        </div>

        <div class="tabs">
            <div class="tab active">Articles</div>
            <div class="tab">About</div>
            <div class="tab">Products</div>
            <div class="tab">Jobs</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Articles -->
        <!-- Jekyll: {% for article in page.company.articles %} -->
        <div class="article">
            <div class="article-header">
                <a href="#" class="article-title">The Future of Cloud Computing: 2024 Trends</a>
                <div class="article-meta">Published by TechCorp Solutions • 3 days ago • 5 min read</div>
            </div>
            <div class="article-content">
                As we move into 2024, cloud computing continues to evolve at a rapid pace. Organizations are increasingly adopting multi-cloud strategies to avoid vendor lock-in and optimize costs. Edge computing is becoming mainstream, bringing processing power closer to data sources...
            </div>
            <div class="article-footer">
                👍 234 likes • 45 comments • 12 shares
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="article">
            <div class="article-header">
                <a href="#" class="article-title">Building Resilient Systems: Best Practices</a>
                <div class="article-meta">Published by TechCorp Solutions • 1 week ago • 8 min read</div>
            </div>
            <div class="article-content">
                System resilience is crucial for modern applications. In this article, we explore key strategies including redundancy, graceful degradation, and chaos engineering. Learn how leading companies build systems that can withstand failures...
            </div>
            <div class="article-footer">
                👍 156 likes • 23 comments • 8 shares
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="article">
            <div class="article-header">
                <a href="#" class="article-title">AI Integration: A Practical Guide for Enterprises</a>
                <div class="article-meta">Published by TechCorp Solutions • 2 weeks ago • 12 min read</div>
            </div>
            <div class="article-content">
                Artificial Intelligence is no longer just a buzzword—it's a business imperative. This comprehensive guide walks through the practical steps of integrating AI into existing enterprise systems, from pilot projects to full-scale deployment...
            </div>
            <div class="article-footer">
                👍 445 likes • 67 comments • 34 shares
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- {% endfor %} -->
    </div>

